  <para>
    Elemental Teal is a combination of the SLE Micro for Rancher with the Rancher Elemental stack.
SLE Micro for Rancher is a containerized and "stripped to the bones" OS layer. At its core, it only requires <command>grub2</command>, <command>dracut</command>, a kernel, and &systemd;.
It's sole purpose is to run Kubernetes (k3s or RKE2), with everything controlled through Rancher Manager.
